<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Medical Terms Valid in Scrabble — High-Scoring Health Vocabulary</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 5 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">Medical vocabulary is a goldmine for Scrabble players. These words often use unusual letter combinations (ZY, PH, XY) that score well and confuse opponents who might challenge perfectly valid terms. From anatomy to pharmacology, here are the medical words worth knowing.</p>

<p>Healthcare professionals have a natural advantage in Scrabble — their everyday vocabulary includes hundreds of valid words that casual players have never encountered. Even if you're not in medicine, learning these terms adds powerful weapons to your arsenal.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Top Scoring Medical Words</h2>

<div class="overflow-x-auto not-prose my-6">
  <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
    <thead class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800">
      <tr>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Word</th>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Points</th>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Category</th>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Meaning</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100 dark:divide-gray-800">
      <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">ZYMOTIC</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">23</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Disease</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Relating to fermentation</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">ZYGOTIC</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">21</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Biology</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Relating to a zygote</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">OXYTOCIN</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">20</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Hormone</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Bonding hormone</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">ZYGOMA</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">21</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Anatomy</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Cheekbone arch</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">QUININE</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">16</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Pharmacology</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Anti-malarial drug</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">THYROID</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">14</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Anatomy</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Neck gland</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Medical Words by Category</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
