    <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-2">🦴 Anatomy</p>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">FEMUR, TIBIA, ULNA, FIBULA, TRACHEA, SPLEEN, THYMUS, CORTEX, AORTA, ZYGOMA</p>
  </div>
